          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "  -the radiochemical separation of I-124 from",
                "natural Sb was by distillation of iodine using conc.",
                "sulphuric acid saturated with sodium nitrite as a",
                "solvent for the target, CCl(4) as a trap and 100 mug",
                "of KI as a carrier.",
                "  -in the separation of I-124 from enriched Te-124",
                "target, the same procedure is used except that only",
                "sulphuric acid is used to dissolve the target. The",
                "distillation procedure takes about 30 minutes and at",
                "the end of this period over 90% of the I-124 distils",
                "into the CCl(4) trap. Finally I-124 is extracted from",
                "CCl(4) with 0.5 ml of 0.01 M NaOH solution."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDEG"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " the deuteron beam of 20 MeV available from the",
                "cyclotron is degraded in energy to 15 MeV by using high",
                "purity Al foils. The energy window used for the",
                "production of I-124 is from 15 to 8 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " in the case of I-125 measurement. I-125 was",
                "monitored by comparing the ratio of the 28 keV iodine",
                "X-ray to the 35 keV gamma-ray of I-125 in a pure I-125",
                "sample and in the produced I-124."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " The data was corrected for decay occurring between",
                " EOB and counting times."
              ]
            }
          ],
